| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6939 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 31e658e2-6dd4-5ca5-aaa7-c2df1d42ad69"
